description: With the "Warranty Manager" you are be able to manage the warranties of your bought devices. Enter all necessary data (name, manufacturer, date, price and so on) and just save it. Optionally you can create a calendar reminder which automatically reminds you if your warranty expires and/or take a picture of the product. You want to delete a product? Just swipe and delete the entry in the list. The list is long and you search for anything? Just type in what you are searching for and the list filters it self.
